{"tid":1853540,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大研發新款防菌布口罩　可洗可重用70次替代一盒外科口罩","createTime":"2020-01-31T04:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T05:23:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c59b492e780c9d4d583aa90250cac311de14ba2c","tid":1853540,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"全城一罩難求，連日有大批市民為購買口罩，冒着寒冷凌晨排隊，政府卻無任何措施幫助解決口罩荒。自由黨黨魁、紡織及製衣界立法會議員鍾國斌今早接受港台訪問時，指已與理大正研發一款新的布口罩，可以清洗及重用50至70次，相等於一盒或盒半的外科口罩。他又說，正安排將內地原材料運往香港，在香港本地生產，最快十多日後就可供應。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌說，雖然政務司司長張建宗昨日稱未來共有3千萬個口罩來港，但全港一個月起碼要2億個口罩，如疫情持續數個月，供應量永遠未必足夠香港需求，故與理大正研發新的布口罩。他指該款布料原本用於防菌衣服，如運動服等，未曾用作製作口罩，但該布料可做到防菌、抑菌及殺菌，可清洗及重用，可以使用近兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n他指該款布料已有國際認證，由理大研發，是政府數年前給予理大科研的資助成果，經過檢測肯定可防範肺炎鏈球菌、金黃葡萄球菌、念珠菌等，但未曾進行新型冠狀病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n鍾續稱，正在製作樣版，周一會完成，如計算到製作材料用量，即可以知道現時的材料量可製作多少口罩，相信有約萬個，冀盡快下周可落實。他亦說，在這個急切情況下不會計算成本，坦言新物料一定昂貴，但希望製作首批後可免費送予長者及弱勢社群。<br />\n<br />\n被問到政府在今次疫症表現，鍾國斌狠批「慢十拍」，形容相比下，澳門政府果斷，又指港府應暫停中國旅客入境香港至少14日，若疫情持續，再延長禁止入境的日期。"},{"pid":"9bafb7f789d2eb806f127f37a1916d3b63c159a9","tid":1853540,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200131/7Y7NHMFB2SLWUR5C6RUY2D2OEQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200131%2F7Y7NHMFB2SLWUR5C6RUY2D2OEQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=a5552b39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200131%2F7Y7NHMFB2SLWUR5C6RUY2D2OEQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a108785f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200131/7Y7NHMFB2SLWUR5C6RUY2D2OEQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"3e6bd88d91e06ee113b3e7541bc28941df32a753","tid":1853540,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"內地原材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0de0ef56ebb6f4b42ff5ee7e4c3dfe5c04dfeb","tid":1853540,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92f5a70d566b9cdc7ce030a51bc68f95f51af59","tid":1853540,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:49:31.000Z","msg":"【疫情展望】手足做好防護措施，去到 Phase II. 就仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n祝各位手足身體健康"},{"pid":"c9105bfc88e5b3425ff0f8039db8723f9fce9cc0","tid":1853540,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警報 <br />\n呢啲議題 真心高汁<br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"efc418d54406d79421d56f351041cc7f0c3db305","tid":1853540,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T04:51:08